Version:    0.0.1
License:    MIT
Author:     Fedor Gogolev <knsd@knsd.net>

Stability:  Experimental
Category:   API
Build-type: Simple
Synopsis:   Rosalind soulutions

Cabal-version: >= 1.2
Tested-with:   GHC==7.4.*

Library
